NK005(ca)007:0: dpal he ru ka'i thugs kyi rgyud gal po zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK005(ca)007:2: sh+r+ai he ru ka tsit+ta tan+t+ra kalpa n+aa ma /
NK005(ca)007:4: dpal he ru ka'i thugs kyi rgyud gal po zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)007:5: dpal 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)007:6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK005(ca)007:7: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK005(ca)007:8: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga
NK005(ca)007:9: la bzhugs so // de'i tshe brjod kyis mi lang
NK005(ca)007:10: ba'i yang brjod kyis mi lang ba'i 'khor la 'di
NK005(ca)007:11: la bzhugs so // lta ste / lnga dang gsum dang brgyad gnyis dang //
NK005(ca)007:12: bzhi dang gcig dang bzhi bcu gcig /
NK005(ca)007:14: rin chen mchog phran yon tan brgyan //
NK005(ca)007:15: sh+r+ai ni gnyis med ston pa'i don //
NK005(ca)007:16: he ni dgyes pa'i gad mo ste //
NK005(ca)007:17: ru ni chags pa chen po'i don //
NK005(ca)007:18: ka ni ye shes phrin las bzhi //
NK005(ca)007:19: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin sku //
NK005(ca)007:20: lus kyi rnam shes gzugs sku rnam snang mdzad //
NK005(ca)007:21: gti mug rnam dag yang dag bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)007:22: kun gzhi'i rnam shes mi bskyod rdo rje sems //
NK005(ca)007:23: zhe sdang rab grub bcom ldan 'das kyi sku //
NK005(ca)007:24: nyon mongs rnam shes tshor ba rin chen 'byung //
NK005(ca)007:25: nga rgyal rang grub gcig pu bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)007:26: yid kyi rnam shes 'du shes snang mtha' yas //
NK005(ca)007:27: 'dod chags rang byung sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)007:28: sgo lnga'i rnam shes 'du byed don yod grub //
NK005(ca)007:29: phrag dog rang byung rnal 'byor bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)007:30: kun gzhi'i rnam shes rang byung dpal chen nyid //
NK005(ca)007:31: dug lnga rang byung kun 'dus bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)007:32: rnal 'byor zab mo'i ngang du sku gsum rdzogs //
NK005(ca)007:33: yang dag grub pa chos sku gcig nyid ni //
NK005(ca)007:34: ye nas dag pa chos kyi sku //
NK005(ca)007:35: lhun gyis gnas pa'i longs spyod rdzogs //
NK005(ca)007:36: 'joms byed ces bya'i dam tshig ni //
NK005(ca)007:37: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:38: phung po lnga nyid rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK005(ca)007:39: nyon mongs pa ni gnas su dag /
NK005(ca)007:40: skye 'jig med pa'i gnas la bzhugs //
NK005(ca)007:41: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde //
NK005(ca)007:42: tsham rngams drag pos lha chen 'dar zhing bardzisa //
NK005(ca)007:43: brtul zhugs rol pas rdos bcas phung po bshig /
NK005(ca)007:44: rnam shes mi 'chi rgyal ba'i gnas su stobs //
NK005(ca)007:45: nyon mongs mi spang sha rus khrag la rol //
NK005(ca)007:46: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus dpal gyi sku //
NK005(ca)007:47: spos mod dkar ser chom rkun rmongs byed ma //
NK005(ca)007:48: mthing dang ljang sogs chags pas khro bar byed //
NK005(ca)007:49: rdo rje mkha' la 'gro ba'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK005(ca)007:50: dpal gyi bka' nyan lhag mar dbang ba bdun //
NK005(ca)007:51: 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs ye shes +aa ra li //
NK005(ca)007:52: gzhi lam 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK005(ca)007:53: rnam pa gsum gyi don bshad do //
NK005(ca)007:54: he ru ka thugs kyi gal po las /
NK005(ca)007:55: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NK005(ca)007:57: // de nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag pos /
NK005(ca)007:58: de bzhin gshegs pa nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa'i
NK005(ca)007:59: de bzhin gshegs pa'i btsun mo'i b+ha ga la dam
NK005(ca)007:60: tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhir byin gyis brlabs
NK005(ca)007:61: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas rig
NK005(ca)007:62: pa'i skyes bu chen po'i gzugs /
NK005(ca)007:63: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po 'di byin gyis brlabs so //
NK005(ca)007:64: byin gyis brlabs ma thag tu byang chub sems kyi
NK005(ca)007:65: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa zhal gsum pa lta
NK005(ca)007:66: bur gyur te / de la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gzigs par gyur to //
NK005(ca)007:67: de'i tshe nam mkha'i dbyings na bzhugs pa'i sems can ji snyed pa de dag /
NK005(ca)007:68: byang chub kyi sems rdo rje'i byin gyis rlabs kyis bde ba dang yid bde ba thob ste /
NK005(ca)007:69: de nas bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa la sogs pa thams cad ngo mtshar che ste /
NK005(ca)007:70: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang la ngam zhing bstod do //
NK005(ca)007:71: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus te /
NK005(ca)007:72: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad rab tu grub pa zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)007:73: byang chub kyi snying por zhugs pa gang na ba der gshegs te /
NK005(ca)007:74: byang chub sems dpa' de la ched du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bstan nas /
NK005(ca)007:76: rigs kyi bu khyod gang gi phyin yin /
NK005(ca)007:77: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK005(ca)007:78: kyi de nyid rtogs par bya ba'i phyir dbang gi
NK005(ca)007:80: rang bzhin lhun grub ye dkyil du //
NK005(ca)007:81: slob ma rab gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)007:82: bya bral ye rdzogs man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)007:84: slob ma 'bring gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)007:85: bskyed rdzogs bsgrub pa'i man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)007:86: gzugs brnyan bsnyen bsgrub dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:87: tha ma'i slob gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK005(ca)007:88: rim gyis bslab sbyang man ngag bstan //
NK005(ca)007:89: rdo rje'i tshul du dbang dag sbyin //
NK005(ca)007:90: lha mo dag dang gar byed cing //
NK005(ca)007:91: der ni rab dgyes bdag po khrid //
NK005(ca)007:92: pho brang dag byed rab dgyes che //
NK005(ca)007:93: rab dgyes bdag po de thob ldan //
NK005(ca)007:94: seng ge'i bden rab 'joms byed cing //
NK005(ca)007:95: gzhi dang gzhi yi mchog nyid kyis //
NK005(ca)007:96: rdo rje pad+mara ldan byas te //
NK005(ca)007:97: dbyings kyi bde chen de las so //
NK005(ca)007:98: g.yon phyogs gnas la tshul bzhin du //
NK005(ca)007:99: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
NK005(ca)007:100: dkyil 'khor zla gam zhes gsungs te //
NK005(ca)007:101: mchog nyid yid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK005(ca)007:102: gzhal yas khang chen ye shes te //
NK005(ca)007:104: sgo bzhi dran pa nyer gzhag bzhi //
NK005(ca)007:105: rnam thar brgyad dang rta babs so //
NK005(ca)007:106: rin chen sgo stegs thugs rje'i ngang //
NK005(ca)007:107: yang dag spong bzhi t+aa ra na //
NK005(ca)007:108: dran pa nyer gzhag sgo khyud dang //
NK005(ca)007:109: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i sgo khyams dang //
NK005(ca)007:110: phreng ba byang chub yan lag bdun //
NK005(ca)007:111: 'phags lam brgyad kyi ka bas mdzes //
NK005(ca)007:112: lam gyi ye shes rnga yab dang //
NK005(ca)007:114: dril bu ba dan rlung bskyod pa //
NK005(ca)007:115: shes rab chos kyi sgra sgrogs dang //
NK005(ca)007:116: che ba'i yon tan 'dus pa'i rtags //
NK005(ca)007:117: bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i rgyal mtshan dang //
NK005(ca)007:118: thod phreng sku gsum thob pa'i rtags //
NK005(ca)007:119: gzhal yas khang mchog dam pa der //
NK005(ca)007:120: phan dang nus mthu'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK005(ca)007:121: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK005(ca)007:122: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK005(ca)007:123: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK005(ca)007:124: snying po lnga dang nus pa lnga //
NK005(ca)007:125: gsang ba'i dbang gsum byin byas la //
NK005(ca)007:126: dbang bskur man ngag snying por sbyin //
NK005(ca)007:127: sa lam rim gyis rab tu bgrod //
NK005(ca)007:128: bla med mi spang bya ma bkur //
NK005(ca)007:129: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK005(ca)007:130: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK005(ca)007:131: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK005(ca)007:132: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK005(ca)007:133: bsgrub dang srung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK005(ca)007:134: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK005(ca)007:135: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK005(ca)007:136: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi sha chen dang //
NK005(ca)007:137: dag pa'i snod chu mi 'dor ro //
NK005(ca)007:138: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig ste //
NK005(ca)007:139: ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyad //
NK005(ca)007:140: dam tshig nyams pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:142: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga nyid las //
NK005(ca)007:143: gcig la gnyis dang bcu phrag gsum //
NK005(ca)007:144: he ru ka gal po zhes bya ba'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:145: dbang dang dam tshig bstan pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:147: // de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NK005(ca)007:148: mdo bsdus ba ste rgyas par min //
NK005(ca)007:149: grub pa dang ni rab tu bsgrub //
NK005(ca)007:150: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu blang bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:151: zhi ba'i dgon gnas lha yi gnas //
NK005(ca)007:152: ri bo chen po 'dus pa'i rtser //
NK005(ca)007:153: gangs dkar shel gyis gtams pa'i 'dabs //
NK005(ca)007:154: seng chen khros pa'i gnas dang ni //
NK005(ca)007:155: tsan+dana nags dang me tog tshal //
NK005(ca)007:156: yid 'ong dben par rab tu bshad //
NK005(ca)007:157: khro bo'i dgon gnas srin po'i gnas //
NK005(ca)007:158: ri bo chen po btsan po'i ngos //
NK005(ca)007:159: brag dmar gtams pa'i dkyiil ngos la //
NK005(ca)007:160: stag dred 'thab pa'i gnas su bya //
NK005(ca)007:161: ma mo'i dgon gnas dur khrod dang //
NK005(ca)007:162: shin tu dben pa'i sa phyogs na //
NK005(ca)007:163: gsar rnying dbugs bral ma bdun khyim //
NK005(ca)007:164: rdo rje rigs kyi dgon gnas ni //
NK005(ca)007:165: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang //
NK005(ca)007:166: ma mo'i khyim dang yid du 'ong //
NK005(ca)007:167: der ni sa yi cho ga dang //
NK005(ca)007:168: phyi nang las kyi rim pa brtsam //
NK005(ca)007:169: gnas su phyin la mtshams gsum bcad //
NK005(ca)007:170: ma dag bshags pa'i bya ba dang //
NK005(ca)007:171: b+ha lan sku yi sbyor ba yis //
NK005(ca)007:172: bsgral zhing mnan pa'i las kyang brtsam //
NK005(ca)007:173: dben pa'i gnas su bla ma la //
NK005(ca)007:174: dam tshig dbang gis brtul zhugs nod //
NK005(ca)007:175: thig le zla gam gcig pa ru //
NK005(ca)007:176: dmigs rten mngon par bzhag nas su //
NK005(ca)007:177: sems nyid gnas pa'i bya ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)007:178: thabs kyi ngo bo thams cad dam //
NK005(ca)007:179: de bzhin srog dang rtsa las byung //
NK005(ca)007:180: rang gi lha yi cha byad du //
NK005(ca)007:181: sgrub pa'i phyag rgya rab tu bya //
NK005(ca)007:182: char sprin mdog 'dra dpa' bo'i gzugs //
NK005(ca)007:183: shin tu gtum po 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)007:184: yang na gtso bo gcig pu bri //
NK005(ca)007:185: slob dpon dang ni slob bu dang //
NK005(ca)007:186: gnas dang yo byad ldan gyur nas //
NK005(ca)007:187: sgrub pa'i las la gzhug par bya //
NK005(ca)007:188: bslang dang brtag dang sbyang ba dang //
NK005(ca)007:189: bgegs bskrad sa bzung dpang po gzhag /
NK005(ca)007:190: 'jig rten sa bdag lha klu la //
NK005(ca)007:191: sa rin gzhal te sa bslang sbyang //
NK005(ca)007:192: rnam par rtog pa bgegs yin te //
NK005(ca)007:193: bgegs ni rang gi sems las byung //
NK005(ca)007:194: sems la rang bzhin med shes na //
NK005(ca)007:195: gzhan na bgegs zhes bya ba med //
NK005(ca)007:196: shes rab kyis ni rnam bshad bya //
NK005(ca)007:197: cod pan bde gshegs lngar bsgom na //
NK005(ca)007:198: sangs rgyas kyis kyang gnod mi nus //
NK005(ca)007:199: btab pa tsam gyis bgegs 'phen byed //
NK005(ca)007:200: zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting 'dzin gyi //
NK005(ca)007:201: gnas bsrung ba ni rab tu bya //
NK005(ca)007:202: g.yas kyi spyan zur bzlog pa las //
NK005(ca)007:203: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsam par bya //
NK005(ca)007:204: gu lang dbang chen nye dbang dang //
NK005(ca)007:205: u ma gshin rje tshangs par bcas //
NK005(ca)007:206: thams cad ma lus sreg par byed //
NK005(ca)007:207: zla bas gso bar byed pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:208: ka ta ra li 'bar spro zhing //
NK005(ca)007:209: mtshon cha 'bar ba'i sa bon gyis //
NK005(ca)007:210: thams cad ma lus bsal bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:211: sangs rgyas kun gyi ting nge 'dzin //
NK005(ca)007:212: stong pa nyid ces rgyal pas gsungs //
NK005(ca)007:213: de bas rnam pa thams cad du //
NK005(ca)007:214: thams cad tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs //
NK005(ca)007:215: pho brang lha dang dmigs pa'i yul //
NK005(ca)007:216: rdo rje thod pa'i sbyor ba dang //
NK005(ca)007:217: chags pa chen po'i yul du bya //
NK005(ca)007:218: dur khrod gnas kyi sa blangs la //
NK005(ca)007:219: stegs bu 'dom gang gru bzhi pa //
NK005(ca)007:220: steng du khru gang pa yi tshad //
NK005(ca)007:221: ba byung sna lngas skyang nul bya //
NK005(ca)007:222: rang byung lnga yi khyad par las //
NK005(ca)007:223: sa bon ye shes lnga ru rdzogs //
NK005(ca)007:224: dkyil 'khor zla gam sgo gcig pa //
NK005(ca)007:225: shar du bstan pa byas nas su //
NK005(ca)007:226: kha dog sdug gu'i tshon gyis bri //
NK005(ca)007:227: chos kun rtsa ba sems yin te //
NK005(ca)007:228: sems kyi rtsa ba gsum du shar //
NK005(ca)007:229: de nyid gzhal yas gnyis dang lha //
NK005(ca)007:230: mi rtsol bde bar rab 'bad pas //
NK005(ca)007:231: snying rje chen pos 'gro don mdzad //
NK005(ca)007:232: thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyu las ni //
NK005(ca)007:233: 'byung ba lnga yi phra bkod pas //
NK005(ca)007:234: yum lnga rnam dag mkha' dbyings te //
NK005(ca)007:235: ma bcos lhun grub yum gyi mkha' //
NK005(ca)007:236: rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas rnam par dag /
NK005(ca)007:237: bzhi po rtsa ba yan lag dang //
NK005(ca)007:238: rigs dang sku mdog phyag mtshan dang //
NK005(ca)007:239: yi ge snying po phyag rgyal ldan //
NK005(ca)007:240: go rim gdan dang rgyan lugs dang //
NK005(ca)007:241: bzhugs thabs tshul dang bcu bzhi yis //
NK005(ca)007:242: zhi ba'i las rnams bskyed par bya //
NK005(ca)007:243: mi skyod mthing ga dkar dmar zhal //
NK005(ca)007:244: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK005(ca)007:245: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK005(ca)007:246: dbyings phyugs g.yas b+han g.yon dril sngo //
NK005(ca)007:247: dkyil 'khor lnga dang ldan par sgom //
NK005(ca)007:248: spyan drang mchod bstod la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)007:249: ji ltar rim pa bzhin du bya //
NK005(ca)007:250: spros med bar mar rab tu khros //
NK005(ca)007:251: blo yi rim pas bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)007:252: tshom bu lnga yi man+dala la //
NK005(ca)007:254: dang por stong nyid rnam bsam ste //
NK005(ca)007:255: lus can kun gyi dri ma bkru //
NK005(ca)007:256: gru gsum mthing nag nam mkha' la //
NK005(ca)007:257: 'degs byed rlung nag rgya gram gtams //
NK005(ca)007:259: keng rus ri rab brtsegs pa'i steng //
NK005(ca)007:260: dur khrod me ri smug nag 'bar //
NK005(ca)007:261: zla gam dbang chen man+dala la //
NK005(ca)007:262: dur khrod yon tan tshogs kyis brgyan //
NK005(ca)007:263: phyi dang nang med rab tu gsal //
NK005(ca)007:264: ye shes gzhal yas nam mkha'i rgya //
NK005(ca)007:265: b+h+r+aumm bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)007:266: dpal stobs nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK005(ca)007:267: rdo rje dbyings las dpal gyi skur bsgyur ba //
NK005(ca)007:268: dwangs pa'i mtsho la rlabs chen 'khrugs pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)007:269: zhi ba'i sku las khro bo'i phyag rgyar bstan //
NK005(ca)007:270: gcig dgu nyi shu gnyis dang lnga bcu brgyad //
NK005(ca)007:271: 'bar ba'i rgyal po cir yang ston par mdzad //
NK005(ca)007:272: bsgrub dang gsang sngags spyod pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:273: grub pa dang ni gnas bdag dang //
NK005(ca)007:274: bzlas pa'i sgra yang phyag rgyar rtogs //
NK005(ca)007:276: dbus su rgyal rigs dum bu gcig /
NK005(ca)007:277: phyogs bzhir bram ze rgyal rigs dang //
NK005(ca)007:278: rje'u rigs dmangs rigs bzhi la bya //
NK005(ca)007:279: mtshams bzhir khrus kyi mkhan po dang //
NK005(ca)007:280: rje rigs btso blag mkhan rnams dal //
NK005(ca)007:281: mi yi khrag la snag tsha bya //
NK005(ca)007:282: mchog gi rkang gi smyug gu yis //
NK005(ca)007:283: lha dgu so so'i snying po bri //
NK005(ca)007:284: rab tu mtshan gsol bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)007:285: zla gam dkyil 'khor yum gyi mkha' //
NK005(ca)007:286: b+han+d+ha bde gshegs sku yi sku //
NK005(ca)007:287: yig 'bru bde gshegs gsung gi gsung //
NK005(ca)007:288: mar me bde gshegs thugs kyi thugs //
NK005(ca)007:289: he ru ka gal po zhes bya ba'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:290: lha rnams 'byung ba bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:292: // de nas yang khrag 'thung chen po de nyid kyis sngags bsdus pa 'di lta bu gsungs so //
NK005(ca)007:293: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)007:302: badz+ra seng ha mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:303: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:304: badz+ra sh+ri g+aa la mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:305: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:308: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:309: badz+ra u l+au ka mu kha he /
NK005(ca)007:310: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahphata /
NK005(ca)007:311: badz+ra a mu kha h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)007:313: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hohphata /
NK005(ca)007:314: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)007:315: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bdag /
NK005(ca)007:316: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)007:317: phyag rgya chen por mngon rdzogs shing //
NK005(ca)007:318: sku gsung thugs su rang dbang bskur //
NK005(ca)007:319: ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK005(ca)007:321: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:322: w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:323: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:324: de nas bcom ldan 'das ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i sngags 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)007:325: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:326: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:327: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:328: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:329: ma h+aa kri t+ya a nush+tha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)007:330: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)007:331: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa ka ru ni ka
NK005(ca)007:332: i dam sa ma ya dzah ba ling+ta grih+na ho
NK005(ca)007:334: pi pa hoh a la la hoh a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)007:335: mkha' 'gro'i ming dang gtor sngags sbyar //
NK005(ca)007:336: rdo rje thod chen sha chen dang //
NK005(ca)007:337: glang chen mi dang shugs chen sha /
NK005(ca)007:338: khyi sha bdud rtsi lnga la sogs //
NK005(ca)007:339: me rlung sbyor ba ldan pa yis //
NK005(ca)007:341: dpal he ru ka gal po zhes bya ba'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:342: yi ge'i phreng ba 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:344: // de nas rnam par dag pa bshad par bya ste /
NK005(ca)007:345: rnam shes gzugs tshor 'du shes dang //
NK005(ca)007:347: nam mkha' sa chu me rlung 'joms //
NK005(ca)007:348: mig dang rna ba sna lce rnams //
NK005(ca)007:353: nga rgyal phrag dog 'dod chags dang //
NK005(ca)007:354: ser sna gti mug zhe sdang 'joms //
NK005(ca)007:355: yid kyi rnam shes 'dus byas dang //
NK005(ca)007:356: gsang dbang gsang ba'i rnam shes dang //
NK005(ca)007:357: gsang yul gsum 'dus rtog pa bcom //
NK005(ca)007:358: rtag chad bdag dang mtshan mar 'dzin //
NK005(ca)007:359: rnam dag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bshad //
NK005(ca)007:360: bcu ldan ye shes dpal dagu'o //
NK005(ca)007:361: gnyis ldan zag med yum gyi sku //
NK005(ca)007:362: rnam shes brgyad dag mkha' 'gro brgyad //
NK005(ca)007:363: rnam par shes brgyad sing ha'i sku //
NK005(ca)007:364: rtag chad mu bzhi sgo ma bzhi //
NK005(ca)007:365: snod bcud lha dang gzhal yas khang //
NK005(ca)007:366: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i chos //
NK005(ca)007:367: de ni spang bar bya ba min //
NK005(ca)007:368: theg pa gsum ni spang ba min //
NK005(ca)007:369: ka ta li bzhin yongs su bzung //
NK005(ca)007:370: dpal he ru ka gal po zhes bya ba las /
NK005(ca)007:371: rnam par dag pa bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:373: // de nas de kho na nyid kyi le'u bshad par bya ste /
NK005(ca)007:374: stong dang stong min he ru ka /
NK005(ca)007:375: ngo bo gzugs med sgra sogs bral //
NK005(ca)007:376: myong dang snom dang byed pa po //
NK005(ca)007:377: kun nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK005(ca)007:378: ngang gis rnam par dag pa las //
NK005(ca)007:379: lha dang lha mor gang snang yang //
NK005(ca)007:380: yod pa ma yin rang bzhin bral //
NK005(ca)007:381: khyod kyis srog chags gsad par bya //
NK005(ca)007:382: ma byin par yang blang bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:383: 'dod pa log par g.yems par bya //
NK005(ca)007:384: rdzun gyi tshig kyang smra bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:385: de dag rtsa ba yin shes na //
NK005(ca)007:387: dpal he ru ka gal po las //
NK005(ca)007:388: de kho na nyid kyi le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:390: // de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NK005(ca)007:391: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)007:392: dpal chen khrag 'thung phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)007:393: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK005(ca)007:394: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK005(ca)007:395: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rde'u chung g.yas //
NK005(ca)007:396: dung dmar rgyu zhags khyung khra g.yon //
NK005(ca)007:397: shes rab dbyings ma'i phyag rgya ni //
NK005(ca)007:398: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK005(ca)007:399: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la brten //
NK005(ca)007:400: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK005(ca)007:401: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dbyings kyi rgya //
NK005(ca)007:402: goo r+ai b+han dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK005(ca)007:403: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK005(ca)007:404: pra mo chu srin rgyu mtshan dmar //
NK005(ca)007:405: be t+aa byi za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK005(ca)007:408: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK005(ca)007:410: sing ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK005(ca)007:411: b+y+aa g+h+ri gnan blta bsnol dmar stag /
NK005(ca)007:412: sri la nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK005(ca)007:413: shwa na sha 'drad mthing ga spyang //
NK005(ca)007:415: kang ka zhing phrag snar mgo dmar //
NK005(ca)007:416: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK005(ca)007:417: u l+au mthing tshogs 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK005(ca)007:418: rta mdong dkar mo lcags kyus 'dren /
NK005(ca)007:419: phag gdong nag mo zhags pas chings //
NK005(ca)007:420: nyi zla dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK005(ca)007:421: thal byed mthing nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK005(ca)007:423: dpal he ru ka gal po'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:424: lha rnams kyi sku mdog dang phyag mtshan bstan pa'i le'u bdun pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:426: // de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NK005(ca)007:427: snga ma las ni gnas 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)007:429: phung po rdos bcas bem po de //
NK005(ca)007:430: phyogs bzhis bro bzhis sbyang bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:431: ye shes lha dang mkha' 'gro ma //
NK005(ca)007:432: thugs dam bskang zhing thugs dam bskul //
NK005(ca)007:433: 'bru lnga bkod la lam lnga dgag /
NK005(ca)007:434: khrus bya zla gam nub tu bzhag /
NK005(ca)007:435: de la lha rnams dgod pa ni //
NK005(ca)007:436: rigs lnga yab yum bsam par bya //
NK005(ca)007:437: mdun rgyab gnyis su bsgom pa ni //
NK005(ca)007:438: +aa li k+aa li bsam par bya //
NK005(ca)007:439: rnam shes dbang po yul dus la //
NK005(ca)007:440: sems dpa' yab yum bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)007:441: spyi bo rgyab dang lce yi steng //
NK005(ca)007:442: rkang mthil yan chad thub pa drug /
NK005(ca)007:443: lte ba mjug to mkhal khung gnyis //
NK005(ca)007:444: sgo ba yab yum bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)007:445: rnam smin zag bcas phung po la //
NK005(ca)007:446: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK005(ca)007:448: gnyis don mthar phyin phyag rgya sgrol //
NK005(ca)007:449: cho ga lnga dang yan lag lngas //
NK005(ca)007:450: gang mos bskyed cing rab bsgoms la //
NK005(ca)007:451: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim //
NK005(ca)007:452: phyag 'tshal mchod de gnas pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:454: yang nas yang du sbyang bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:455: yang na khrag 'thung chen po'i sku //
NK005(ca)007:456: bdag nyid rab tu gsal bsgom ste //
NK005(ca)007:457: ro yi bsha' thabs rgyab nas bsha' //
NK005(ca)007:458: khrag 'thung lha tshogs rdzas su ste //
NK005(ca)007:459: glo snying dpal chen yab yum gyi //
NK005(ca)007:460: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
NK005(ca)007:461: rigs bzhi khrag 'thung yab yum rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:462: bum pa bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK005(ca)007:463: dpung pa g.yas g.yon bzhag sha dang //
NK005(ca)007:464: rgyu ma mchin pa mgo sha rnams //
NK005(ca)007:465: rtsa ba'i lha dgu'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK005(ca)007:466: go ro tsa na gzhung pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:467: rkang dang tshil bu sha dang khrag /
NK005(ca)007:468: srog rtsa mkhris pa brgyad rnams ni //
NK005(ca)007:469: mu kha phra min brgyad kyi rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:470: yan lag rnam thar bzhi rnams ni //
NK005(ca)007:471: ye shes sgo ma bzhi yi rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:472: sgal tshigs phrugs re bsde ba ni //
NK005(ca)007:473: dbang mo nyi shu brgyad kyi rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:474: na sag che phra bsdeb pa ni //
NK005(ca)007:475: rang byung khro bo bcu yi rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:476: sha khrag rus pa rkang dang tshil //
NK005(ca)007:477: mkha' la 'gro ba kun gyi rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:478: mtshan dang ldan pa'i b+han+d+ha de //
NK005(ca)007:479: dpal chen bzhugs pa'i rten yang yin //
NK005(ca)007:480: de yi nang du blug pa yang //
NK005(ca)007:481: go ro tsa na dri chen dang //
NK005(ca)007:482: snying dang srog pa rtsa yi khrag /
NK005(ca)007:483: m+aam sa mkhris pa dri chu dang //
NK005(ca)007:484: so dang dbang po rnam lnga dang //
NK005(ca)007:485: de rnams cha ni mnyam pa dag /
NK005(ca)007:486: b+han+d+hara blug pa dngos grub rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:487: barla rkang gnyis dang rje ngar rkang //
NK005(ca)007:488: dung chen 'bud pa'i gling bu bya //
NK005(ca)007:489: dpung pa'i rkang mgo gnyis po la //
NK005(ca)007:490: rak+ta sbreng ba'i gzar bu bya //
NK005(ca)007:491: sha sgor dngos grub gsol byang dang //
NK005(ca)007:492: rdo rje dang ni dril bu dang //
NK005(ca)007:493: bdud rtsi'i bum pa dngos grub rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:494: de bzhin dbang gi bum pa bzhag /
NK005(ca)007:495: ting 'dzin ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)007:496: dmigs pa'i rten yang mngon par bri //
NK005(ca)007:497: 'dod chags ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)007:498: rigs kyi yum yang mngon par gzung //
NK005(ca)007:499: yum rnams kun gyi mtshan ma ni //
NK005(ca)007:500: dmar ser mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can //
NK005(ca)007:501: spyan 'phangs dma' la gzi brjid ldan //
NK005(ca)007:503: dpung mgo mtho la ring ba ni //
NK005(ca)007:504: de bzhin rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK005(ca)007:505: dkar gsal dung mdog sgeg mo'i gzugs //
NK005(ca)007:506: sha rus 'khyil ba rdo rje'i dbyibs //
NK005(ca)007:508: dung can ma yi rigs mchog ste //
NK005(ca)007:509: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK005(ca)007:512: shes rab dang ni blo stobs che //
NK005(ca)007:513: mi zad blo gros sems la 'char //
NK005(ca)007:514: rin chen rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK005(ca)007:515: dkar la dmar chags pad+ma'i mdog /
NK005(ca)007:516: chags pa che shes yid gzhungs pa //
NK005(ca)007:518: mig rtsa dmar zhing dmangs 'phrog pa //
NK005(ca)007:519: pad+ma rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK005(ca)007:520: dmar ljang 'khrug pa'i ngo bo la //
NK005(ca)007:521: khro btson las rab don la brtson //
NK005(ca)007:522: sha rgyus mchu zheng gab par 'dug /
NK005(ca)007:523: lag par rdo rje rgya gram 'chang //
NK005(ca)007:524: las kyi rigs kyi gzungs mar shes //
NK005(ca)007:525: gzhan yang gang dag kha cig tu //
NK005(ca)007:526: ri mo gcig pa de bzhin bya //
NK005(ca)007:527: dur khrod blangs pa'i ras chen la //
NK005(ca)007:528: tshon rtsi spyin me rab tu bzang //
NK005(ca)007:529: sgrub po dam tshig ldan pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:530: 'bri mkhan dag kyang dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)007:531: lha dgu dmigs pa'i rten yang bri //
NK005(ca)007:532: de bzhin sgrub pa po yang bri //
NK005(ca)007:533: rab tu gnas pa rab byas te //
NK005(ca)007:535: gling ngam rang dag'i gnas dag tu //
NK005(ca)007:536: de la bsnyen bkur byed pa la //
NK005(ca)007:537: myur du dngos grub ster la brtson //
NK005(ca)007:538: sgrub dang 'bri mkhan ma yin par //
NK005(ca)007:539: lhag ma kun la bstan pa min //
NK005(ca)007:540: sgrub pa dag la 'bad pa'i tshe //
NK005(ca)007:541: skyes bu rtogs pa'i blo gros can //
NK005(ca)007:542: dad pa'i sems dang ldan pa yis //
NK005(ca)007:543: srog lus man chad rdzas rnams ni //
NK005(ca)007:544: ser sna med pa'i sems kyis dbul //
NK005(ca)007:545: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK005(ca)007:546: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK005(ca)007:547: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK005(ca)007:548: kun tu sna tshogs bla ma la //
NK005(ca)007:549: yon gyi mchog ni rab tu dbul //
NK005(ca)007:550: gang na yongs su gtong dka' ba //
NK005(ca)007:551: de ni mchog tu bshad pa yin //
NK005(ca)007:552: bla ma'i rdzas ni srog ji bzhin //
NK005(ca)007:553: gzhi 'dzin snum 'dra dam tshig rin po che //
NK005(ca)007:554: ma rig tha rgod ko khengs lta bu btul //
NK005(ca)007:555: yang dag don rtogs sems dang chos su 'dres //
NK005(ca)007:556: lus dang srog la babs kyang dam tshig mchog mi gtong //
NK005(ca)007:557: rnal 'byor dbang phyug yon tan brgyad dang ldan //
NK005(ca)007:558: bla ma mchog nyid yin par ngas bshad do //
NK005(ca)007:559: dag pa'i ye shes he ru ka /
NK005(ca)007:560: gnyis med don la rab brtson pa //
NK005(ca)007:561: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug grub //
NK005(ca)007:562: sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra sgrogs pa //
NK005(ca)007:563: des ni dkyil 'khor lha rnams bskyed //
NK005(ca)007:564: zab cing 'brug sgra ltar sgrogs pas //
NK005(ca)007:565: gtum po gdug pa'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK005(ca)007:566: mkhur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pas //
NK005(ca)007:567: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa 'gyed //
NK005(ca)007:568: rdo rje srin po ngur skad kyis //
NK005(ca)007:569: gdug pa thams cad spa yang bkong //
NK005(ca)007:571: gdug pa thams cad rdul du rlog /
NK005(ca)007:572: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul gyis //
NK005(ca)007:573: thams cad ma lus dbang du sdud //
NK005(ca)007:574: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)007:575: stong tsho gsum gyi grangs dag ni //
NK005(ca)007:576: rnal 'byor nyin zhag gang bzla pa //
NK005(ca)007:577: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gis //
NK005(ca)007:578: rig 'dzin thob par gdon mi za //
NK005(ca)007:580: 'jig rten pa dag shi zhes brjod //
NK005(ca)007:581: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis //
NK005(ca)007:582: legs zhes rab tu brjod nas kyang //
NK005(ca)007:584: dpal he ru ka gal po zhes bya ba'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:585: sna tshogs rnam par spyod pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:587: // de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NK005(ca)007:588: thig le gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:589: rdo rje bdud rtsi sgrub pa bshad //
NK005(ca)007:590: phun sum tshogs pa bzhir ldan nas //
NK005(ca)007:591: de nas dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:592: zhi khro spel ma'i dkyil 'khor bri //
NK005(ca)007:593: shar du zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:594: mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma bsham //
NK005(ca)007:595: lho ru rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:596: mar me dgu dang gsol byang bzhag /
NK005(ca)007:597: nub tu dbang gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:598: rdo rje'i tshe dang dngos grub rdzas //
NK005(ca)007:599: byang du drag po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)007:600: bsgral ba'i rdzas mchog bzhag par bya //
NK005(ca)007:601: dbus kyi b+han+d+ha srubs med du //
NK005(ca)007:602: rtsa ba brgyad dang lo ma stong //
NK005(ca)007:603: min pa gsum dang yin pa lnga //
NK005(ca)007:604: skyob dang yan lag nyi shu bdun //
NK005(ca)007:605: kha cher skyes dang tsan+dana dri //
NK005(ca)007:606: gnyis 'thung la sogs sha sna stong //
NK005(ca)007:607: 'bru dang rin chen bcud la sogs //
NK005(ca)007:608: gang yang sman chen min pa ni //
NK005(ca)007:609: rab tu bsgrims te bsgrub par bya //
NK005(ca)007:610: bar chod nyul le dus su bzlog /
NK005(ca)007:611: dus ni yar gyi brgyad la 'jug /
NK005(ca)007:612: spyan drangs rtog pa zlog pa dang //
NK005(ca)007:613: sman nyid zhi khro'i lhar bsams te //
NK005(ca)007:615: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)007:616: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aah ma h+aa
NK005(ca)007:617: su kha dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta d+harma d+h+aa tu
NK005(ca)007:618: +aah +aahh+aum badz+ra a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)007:619: sman nyid lha ru rab sbyangs nas //
NK005(ca)007:620: grogs po dpal la sems stobs che //
NK005(ca)007:621: khro bo'i tshul can ging chen ni //
NK005(ca)007:622: h+aum gi sgra dang ldan pa de //
NK005(ca)007:623: chas brgyad khri bcu lus la 'god //
NK005(ca)007:624: mnga' gsol bton la btag btsag bya //
NK005(ca)007:625: ye shes 'od kyi snang ba dril //
NK005(ca)007:626: dpal chen skur bsgom dbang yang bskur //
NK005(ca)007:627: dkyil 'khor chen por rab bskor zhing //
NK005(ca)007:628: ru lu'i bro dang brab dang bdug /
NK005(ca)007:629: dbus su gzhug la slob dpon gyis //
NK005(ca)007:630: bzhi rgyud ldan pa'i dgongs pa bya //
NK005(ca)007:631: tshogs chen mchod pa rgyun mi gcad //
NK005(ca)007:632: gtsang sbra gsum la gnas par bya //
NK005(ca)007:633: tshogs chen gcig gi bsod nams ni //
NK005(ca)007:634: skye la nyan thos brgyar bsags pas //
NK005(ca)007:635: bcu drug char yang mi phod na //
NK005(ca)007:636: mthar thug pa ni tshogs 'khor lo //
NK005(ca)007:641: rdo rje nyi ma nub nas ni //
NK005(ca)007:642: dngos grub chen po blang bar bya //
NK005(ca)007:643: sman chen 'di yi bsod nams ni //
NK005(ca)007:644: lha gnyan dam skong phrin las 'grub //
NK005(ca)007:645: rig 'dzin bzhi dang sgrub pa brgyad //
NK005(ca)007:646: he ru ka yi gsungs bzhin du //
NK005(ca)007:648: gal te 'di la gzugs yod na //
NK005(ca)007:649: 'jig rten srog chags thams cad kyis //
NK005(ca)007:650: brjod par nus pa ma yin no //
NK005(ca)007:651: rdo rje bdud rtsi sman chen te //
NK005(ca)007:652: gsum du bgos la spyad par bya //
NK005(ca)007:653: mdor na mang po smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)007:654: bde gshegs thams cad mchod pa bas //
NK005(ca)007:655: 'di nyid bsgrub pa'i khyad par ni //
NK005(ca)007:656: lhag pa bas kyang ches lhag go //
NK005(ca)007:657: 'di ma yin pa'i bsod nams ni //
NK005(ca)007:658: gzhan na nam yang yod ma yin //
NK005(ca)007:659: de bas bsgrub pa 'bad par bya //
NK005(ca)007:660: dpal he ru ka'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)007:661: rdo rje bdud rtsi bsgrub pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:663: // de nas khrag 'thung chen po des /
NK005(ca)007:664: de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
NK005(ca)007:671: 'bar ma'i tshogs thams cad yi rangs te /
NK005(ca)007:672: dgyes pa'i gad mo bsgrags te /
NK005(ca)007:673: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK005(ca)007:674: khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i rgyud thugs kyi gal po zhes bya ba rdzogs so //
NK005(ca)007:675: u rgyan gyi mkhan po chen po pad+ma sam b+ha wa dang /
NK005(ca)007:676: lo ts+aa ba dge slong nam mkha'i snying pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:677: nub phyogs u rgyan gyi gnas nas slob dpon h+aum ka ras bton pa'o //
NK005(ca)007:678: rgyud 'di'i bka'i srung ma ni mkha' 'gro ma gtsug
NK005(ca)007:679: gi rgyan gcig ma dang srog gi nyul le ma
NK005(ca)007:681: bka'i dus tshigs dang nyi tshod las 'das na mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis chad pa chod cig /
